'''Durgham Maraee''' (born 1971/72) is a Palestinian businessman, the CEO of [[Wataniya Mobile]], a mobile telephone company in Palestine, since November 2014.
Durgham Maraee has a master's degree and a doctorate from [[Harvard University]] in International Law.<ref name="bloomberg1"/>
Maraee was employed by the [[Boston Consulting Group]] (BCG), before working as the chief investment officer at the [[Palestine Investment Fund]] (PIF).<ref name="bloomberg1"/> He has been the CEO of [[Wataniya Mobile]] since November 2014.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wataniya.ps/en/corporate/management-team |title=Wataniya Mobile - Executive Management |publisher=Wataniya.ps |date= |accessdate=2016-04-10}}</ref>
