{{notability|date=January 2018}} '''Industries et Agro-Ressources''' (also called '''Pôle IAR''') is a [[France|French]] [[business cluster]] created in 2005 and located in [[Hauts-de-France]] and [[Grand Est]]. Its main focus is [[Bioeconomy]]<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.absiskey.com/partenaire/pole-iar-industries-agro-ressources/ pôle IAR - Industries & Agro-Ressources]</ref>.
Since December 2017, its C.E.O is Yvon Le Hénaff<ref>{{fr}}[http://www.lunion.fr/65260/article/2017-12-12/yvon-le-henaff-nouveau-president-du-pole-iar Yvon Le Hénaff nouveau président du pôle IAR]</ref>.
